{"tid":1870674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：有些人惡意散播謠言，唯恐天下不亂，市民不要中圈套。","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T05:03:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"abea62cfcc5337f7421ad62a5dd5a5c54bc37cdd","tid":1870674,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗批評有人在抗疫期間惡意散播謠言，呼籲市民留意政府發放的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，食米、麵食等有足夠存貨，市民無須擔心。他批評有人惡意散播謠言，唯恐天下不亂，形容謠言跟病毒一樣都要全力抗擊，呼籲市民不要中造謠者圈套，應留意政府發放的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，去年在社會動盪及暴力破壞下，香港經濟和社會已受重創，疫情的威脅是雪上加霜，預期經營環境短期內難見好轉，部分行業可能會出現結業潮，失業率會上升，特區政府會提供適切的協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379901&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=cc9a29b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379901&h=fb6f2c2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379901</a>"},{"pid":"f75c91a3d6877e79aa60b9cced269d429cb7c1a1","tid":1870674,"uid":1425,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"有些人=689及其爪牙"},{"pid":"6c80d72890571e8715797be223e0d07cdebecf50","tid":1870674,"uid":48362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:24:56.000Z","msg":"我要攪炒<br />\n理得你死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50fb8a6fab5ece6bf78ba52abd4291d334e6af7","tid":1870674,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"雖然話香港靠外國進口糧食, 但是有啲想興風作浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><